RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: magick, pdftools, locatexec, processx, tools
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Suggests: officer, tinytest, testthat, webshot2
BugReports: https://github.com/ardata-fr/doconv/issues
SystemRequirements: LibreOffice, Microsoft Word
